_sText: This map is designed for me to practice my starter pistols.  I made this to prep for a LAN.  This is my First CS:S map, and my second map ever.  I hope you guys enjoy.  Give me some feed back.  Try not to put more then 5 people on each time.  it is not desinged for anything more then that, but there are 40 SPAWNS for people who want to have some fun.
